 "768312218730772", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031436_768312222064105_2483983745682146754_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=53KKqsP-GxoQ7kNvgF1Y42q&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDD9LZkFDNkNw9eM8NeisL8R2tWa3QyBI5coPaNmg8wCQ&oe=66D5BC1E"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240210-1504414_2.png", "id": "1144388200046417", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003227_1144388210046416_8982093088097178928_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dqBMKKesEi8Q7kNvgHsn9N9&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC38D_RyV8jGzTpRdQoRCRLIdoyX-QLR-UciCa0Nk-n_A&oe=66D59511"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240210-115437.png", "id": "1405118490144295", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75230048_1405118493477628_4689660376237645316_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=o_M6XestEMYQ7kNvgE34ANl&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC608G2P2IkfY0a4e3zyjCzQYPeRUZff_ANae-qPRtckg&oe=66D5A51B"}, {"file_name": "com.ypro.project_y-20240209-2137122.png", "id": "7621650634553270", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75556799_7621650644553269_1655627145384024300_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bhU408Sn2kIQ7kNvgGmTugU&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD8MIEflglT1dM_HV2STwLtGk1aHYSpMn6l5XmmX5QAlw&oe=66D59B1D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Project_Y: Working Title", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This game is the Japanese version.\nIt supports Japanese only.\n\n\"A true ghost story told by a person named Y.\nIt was about an investigation to find out the true meaning of a common self-inflicted urban legend that says, ``If you hear it, you'll be cursed.''\nand...\nThere is a ``sinister existence'' that appears and disappears there.\nThis project reconstructed those interview records as 360\u00b0 videos and produced and developed them as interactive content using live-action VR.\n\n\n- It comes with \"\